Black market
Fieruz, who could help steal the meteorite, has made his way to the Black Market, a secret trading place. Without his help, it is impossible to get meteorite samples. Fieruz must be found.
#subobj 1
Leave the city
The only way out of town, straight to the northern plantations, is almost unguarded.
#subobj 2
Walk across the north bridge
The northern bridge is almost unguarded, but the wild animals behind it pose a serious threat.
#subobj 3
Walk on the west bridge
The western bridge is guarded on both sides - a Khadagan war post is located nearby.
#subobj 4
Go to the black market
On the way to the Black Market you can meet even more adult and strong animals than in the Portal area.